143
00:11:51,960 --> 00:12:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] Evo vidiš, vidiš kako humor je destruktivan, ti sad šta god kažem gotovo, svi samo zamišljaju tebe kako ide po kesice, ono, po kvartu, gotovo.

144
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:05,639
[SPEAKER_00] Završi, najbolje gotovo.

145
00:12:05,639 --> 00:12:13,940
[SPEAKER_02] I vidi ja sam toliko mladih ljudi, ovo je važno, Ante. Toliko mladih ljudi, poput Ante, koji su se uništavali.

146
00:12:13,940 --> 00:12:17,440
[SPEAKER_03] Ideš po deka mortadele, vratiš na samo 10 deka.

147
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:23,919
[SPEAKER_05] Grama, ne deka, šta to nosiš, kese, povati ćete.

148
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:26,419
[SPEAKER_03] Vidi brata kako lijepo nastavljaju.

149
00:12:26,419 --> 00:12:29,539
[SPEAKER_03] I sad kako ti reći nešto ozbiljno samiš.

150
00:12:30,019 --> 00:12:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] A i mater je dobro, zna ti še izi, ne mora mater stjeći, a nis u nabavku.

151
00:12:36,659 --> 00:12:44,259
[SPEAKER_02] I dobro, i stvarno sam, kasnije, kad sam upoznal...

152
00:12:44,259 --> 00:12:50,139
[SPEAKER_03] To ćete me pusti da kažu, evo i s čime sam porin, s čime sam porin.

153
00:12:50,139 --> 00:12:51,639
[SPEAKER_03] I ti ja sam ti ljudima...

154
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:55,500
[SPEAKER_03] Ili ima neke PP ovde?

155
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:56,779
[SPEAKER_03] Možemo reza tako.

156
00:12:56,779 --> 00:12:57,700
[SPEAKER_03] Nema, nema.

157
00:12:57,779 --> 00:13:00,639
[SPEAKER_03] Čekaj, ovo, enako se ne snima, tako...

158
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:03,679
[SPEAKER_03] Aj najaviti, su dvoji.

159
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:05,159
[SPEAKER_03] E, skratič.

160
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:11,039
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, ti ja sam, tim nadim ljudima, došla u meni želja da nonesemo Boga.

161
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:13,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, to je bila neka velika, velika želja.

162
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,919
[SPEAKER_02] Kako? Onako kao mi znamo.

163
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:17,500
[SPEAKER_02] Mi dole, ja sam nekako bija za scenu,

164
00:13:18,259 --> 00:13:23,519
[SPEAKER_02] i to me vuklo, i ne znam, pisa sam neke predstavice za župu i sve, i onda smo nekako išli u tom nekom smjeru.

165
00:13:23,519 --> 00:13:25,860
[SPEAKER_02] Pa i onoj opuštenosti humora.

166
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:29,019
[SPEAKER_02] Vidili smo da ljudi, ljudi dobro reagiraju na smijeh, na humor.

167
00:13:29,019 --> 00:13:35,480
[SPEAKER_02] Nije to meni bilo sad, ja sam humorističan, pa ne, nego vidio sam da je zapravo humor jedan dobar mamac.

168
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:39,200
[SPEAKER_02] Mamac bilo za ljude koji su u crkvi, bilo za one koji su van crkve.

169
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:41,600
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, jednostavno, ljudima kodan nedostaje radosti.

170
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:47,720
[SPEAKER_02] I baš se to poklopilo, recimo sad smo puno razmišljali ovih dana zadnjih, ono, papi Franji,

171
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:51,159
[SPEAKER_02] i kad gledaš njegova prva pobudnica je bila radost evanđelja.

172
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:57,039
[SPEAKER_02] I baš nekako u to slično vrijeme smo nastali, ono, i nadzemljači koju godinu prije čak,

173
00:13:57,039 --> 00:14:01,220
[SPEAKER_02] i kasnije božanstvena, ali baš to, evangelizacija radošću, ono,

174
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:03,679
[SPEAKER_02] radost koja privlači, humor koji privlači.

175
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:12,799
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, to je nekako bila baš znakovita slučajnost da se to dvoje nekako koincidencija.

176
00:14:12,799 --> 00:14:17,120
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, ono, s papom Franjom, dakle, evangelizacija radošću, evangelizacija lajka,

177
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:21,220
[SPEAKER_02] evangelizacija, sve to je nekako, na srcu nam je bilo da mi lajici,

178
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:24,759
[SPEAKER_02] na svoj način, onako možda malo i otkačeni, evo drugima nosimo Bogu.

179
00:14:24,759 --> 00:14:28,179
[SPEAKER_02] A niste imali nikad ono neko dvojbu sa, je, moramo direktnije prenijati poruku?

180
00:14:28,179 --> 00:14:31,460
[SPEAKER_02] Pa imali smo mi uvijek i na tim susretima nadzemlja,

181
00:14:31,519 --> 00:14:34,840
[SPEAKER_02] imali uvijek neko predavanje, nekog predavača i nekog...

182
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:38,059
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, nije to nikad bilo samo humor, pa ni u božanstvenom komediji

183
00:14:38,059 --> 00:14:39,620
[SPEAKER_02] nije nikad samo skeć, samo humor.

184
00:14:39,620 --> 00:14:43,460
[SPEAKER_02] To nekad ljudi previde za to što gledaju samo skećeve koji su izdvojeni,

185
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:44,779
[SPEAKER_02] ono, kasnije na internetu.

186
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:49,480
[SPEAKER_02] Uvijek je to popraćeno i nekim poprilično ozbiljnim razgovorom

187
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:51,100
[SPEAKER_02] s nekim predavačem, gostom.

188
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:54,980
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da nije nama nikad jedna stvar bila najvažnija,

189
00:14:54,980 --> 00:14:57,279
[SPEAKER_02] nije nama najvažniji humor, ali je jako važan.

190
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:59,279
[SPEAKER_02] I vidimo da ljudima jako treba i ljudi...

191
00:14:59,279 --> 00:15:02,340
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, ti kažeš, malo ljudi se bavi time i dan danas istina.

192
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:03,279
[SPEAKER_02] I malo, meni je žao.

193
00:15:03,279 --> 00:15:05,639
[SPEAKER_02] Mi ne mislimo da smo vrhu nas humora.

194
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:07,759
[SPEAKER_02] Mi nas je jedan svoj nesavršen način,

195
00:15:07,759 --> 00:15:11,200
[SPEAKER_02] dajemo sebe tu, pokušavamo i nasmijat ljude,

196
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:13,059
[SPEAKER_02] nekad uspijemo, nekad možda ne uspijemo.

197
00:15:13,059 --> 00:15:15,860
[SPEAKER_02] Mi bismo voljeli da bude još takvih ljudi u crkvi

198
00:15:15,860 --> 00:15:19,440
[SPEAKER_02] koji su i bolji od nas, i smišniji, i humorističniji,

199
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:22,080
[SPEAKER_02] i duhoviti da dođu i da rade neke slične programe.

200
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,759
[SPEAKER_02] Ja osobno mislim i dan danas,

201
00:15:23,759 --> 00:15:26,740
[SPEAKER_02] kad gledam cijelo ovo razdoblje za njih, ne znam, deseta godina,

202
00:15:26,740 --> 00:15:29,899
[SPEAKER_02] da baš nedostaje i da baš treba takog sadržaja.

203
00:15:29,899 --> 00:15:32,740
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ti kao onaj probiotik za dicu što se daje,

204
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] ona čokolada, a unutra je probiotik.

205
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,779
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i mi.

206
00:15:35,779 --> 00:15:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš poruku, ali zamotaš čokoladu od humora

207
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:42,360
[SPEAKER_00] da se dite poveseli i da zagrize.

208
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,759
[SPEAKER_05] Mi smo kao probiotika, a unutra je čokolada.

209
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:48,159
[SPEAKER_05] Dite ima dobija ki lepi da se odakle ovo,

210
00:15:48,159 --> 00:15:48,940
[SPEAKER_05] ja sam obro bi otkaj.

211
00:15:48,940 --> 00:15:52,220
[SPEAKER_05] Ja, drugo smo toga snimili godine,

212
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,840
[SPEAKER_05] ono, stotine, ja mislim, skećeva,

213
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:55,779
[SPEAKER_05] ono, pesto, šest, sedam, ne znam,

214
00:15:55,779 --> 00:15:57,059
[SPEAKER_05] koliko toga ti kratki formi,

215
00:15:57,059 --> 00:15:59,340
[SPEAKER_05] i dobar dio njih je,

216
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:01,960
[SPEAKER_05] bram tamo u početicima, prošao relativno

217
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,679
[SPEAKER_05] nezamijećeno, ili smo ih snimili

218
00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:06,360
[SPEAKER_05] sa nedostatnom

219
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,679
[SPEAKER_05] vizijom,

220
00:16:07,679 --> 00:16:09,279
[SPEAKER_05] tehničko, kako to izvesti,

221
00:16:09,279 --> 00:16:11,299
[SPEAKER_05] pa su neke odlične fore prošle,

222
00:16:11,299 --> 00:16:13,860
[SPEAKER_05] a nije skeć, bože da skeć bio predugačak

223
00:16:13,860 --> 00:16:15,159
[SPEAKER_05] ili ovakv, ali sve o svemu je to bilo

224
00:16:15,159 --> 00:16:17,019
[SPEAKER_05] dosta dobro, ali ipak je bilo jedan dio

225
00:16:17,019 --> 00:16:18,360
[SPEAKER_05] s kojim ja nisam sasvim zadovoljan,

226
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,799
[SPEAKER_05] pričali smo o tom više puta,

227
00:16:19,799 --> 00:16:21,600
[SPEAKER_05] koje smo mogli komprimirati,

228
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,279
[SPEAKER_05] napraviti od njih,

229
00:16:22,279 --> 00:16:23,659
[SPEAKER_05] tako da sad već razgovaramo

230
00:16:23,659 --> 00:16:24,940
[SPEAKER_05] da ove stare epizode uzmemo,

231
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,039
[SPEAKER_05] pa održemo za ove nove

232
00:16:26,039 --> 00:16:27,480
[SPEAKER_05] tiktokovske generacije,

233
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:28,159
[SPEAKER_05] da ih malo...

234
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:29,460
[SPEAKER_02] A ne samo to, ima dobrog sadržaja,

235
00:16:29,460 --> 00:16:31,879
[SPEAKER_02] koji jednostavno nije došao do ljudi,

236
00:16:31,879 --> 00:16:33,120
[SPEAKER_02] jer kad smo počinjali,

237
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,500
[SPEAKER_02] to je bilo poprilično novo

238
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:36,440
[SPEAKER_02] i trebalo je malo ljudima da

239
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,200
[SPEAKER_02] saznaju za nas,

240
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,740
[SPEAKER_02] da vide što to radimo,

241
00:16:39,740 --> 00:16:42,000
[SPEAKER_02] tako da ima i dobrih fora,

242
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,580
[SPEAKER_02] ali koje nisu jednostavno...

243
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:45,259
[SPEAKER_00] Navike ljudi su se jako promijenili

244
00:16:45,259 --> 00:16:46,220
[SPEAKER_00] u jednjih deset godina,

245
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:48,220
[SPEAKER_00] znači da sad vratiš prije deset godina,

246
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] šta je bio nekakav normalni sadržaj

247
00:16:50,059 --> 00:16:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] koji prolazi na internetu,

248
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] sad ti je to negledljivo

249
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu trajanja, recimo,

250
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] bilo kakvog sadržaja.

251
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] Znači sve mora biti kraće.

252
00:16:57,139 --> 00:16:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je sve, ono,

253
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:00,080
[SPEAKER_00] baš taj skok je abnormalan

254
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] u zadnjih deset godina,

255
00:17:01,039 --> 00:17:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] znači doslovno,

256
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] sad da upališ bilo šta,

257
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] od tada izgleda sporo.

258
00:17:05,779 --> 00:17:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, mi možemo isto uzeti nešto naše

259
00:17:08,259 --> 00:17:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] i onda, ajmo reći,

260
00:17:09,559 --> 00:17:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] nekako to reciklirati

261
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,799
[SPEAKER_00] da s tehničke strane

262
00:17:11,799 --> 00:17:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] bude ljudima prijemčljivije.

263
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,119
[SPEAKER_05] Sada je pitanje kako to da se publika

264
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,859
[SPEAKER_05] toliko promijenila,

265
00:17:16,859 --> 00:17:18,799
[SPEAKER_05] uzmijenite reke skeće od Monty Pythona stare,

266
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:22,720
[SPEAKER_05] koji su, recimo, onako sadržajni i bogati,

267
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,599
[SPEAKER_05] ali nekako ti dinamika

268
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:26,799
[SPEAKER_05] i se gubi ne monoga nekakvog sažetog,

269
00:17:26,799 --> 00:17:27,940
[SPEAKER_05] nego traju posljedno 8 minuta,

270
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:28,519
[SPEAKER_05] samo pričaju,

271
00:17:28,519 --> 00:17:29,660
[SPEAKER_05] dok ih pohvataš.

272
00:17:29,660 --> 00:17:30,980
[SPEAKER_05] Ja znam dosta prijatelja

273
00:17:30,980 --> 00:17:32,259
[SPEAKER_05] koji kažu, više mi to nije smiješno,

274
00:17:32,259 --> 00:17:34,240
[SPEAKER_05] a prije je bilo smiješno,

275
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,279
[SPEAKER_05] pa se je publika promijenila

276
00:17:35,279 --> 00:17:38,039
[SPEAKER_05] ili je samo to džije,

277
00:17:38,039 --> 00:17:39,039
[SPEAKER_05] samo je to kao stil novi

278
00:17:39,039 --> 00:17:40,079
[SPEAKER_05] koji nam više ili manje odgovara.

279
00:17:40,079 --> 00:17:41,519
[SPEAKER_04] Dobro, ali, ok,

280
00:17:41,519 --> 00:17:42,400
[SPEAKER_04] pričali smo sad

281
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,200
[SPEAKER_04] kak je to u stvari evangelizacijski projekti

282
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:45,200
[SPEAKER_04] ili to donijet Boga ljudima.

283
00:17:46,039 --> 00:17:47,839
[SPEAKER_04] imali sad dosta dobar prolaz

284
00:17:47,839 --> 00:17:49,680
[SPEAKER_04] prema ljudima koji nisu toliko bili u crkvi.

285
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,539
[SPEAKER_04] Ok, mene zanima,

286
00:17:51,539 --> 00:17:53,859
[SPEAKER_04] a jeste imali negativnih komentara,

287
00:17:53,859 --> 00:17:55,720
[SPEAKER_04] pretpostavljam, od nas

288
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:57,240
[SPEAKER_04] koji smo, evo, tu u crkvi,

289
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:59,099
[SPEAKER_04] pa sad, evo, kako možete na taj način?

290
00:17:59,099 --> 00:18:01,119
[SPEAKER_04] Odnosno, mogu publikovati pitanje.

291
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,700
[SPEAKER_04] Ili možete prokomentirati

292
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,319
[SPEAKER_04] da li se u tim svetim stvarima

293
00:18:05,319 --> 00:18:06,220
[SPEAKER_04] kad pričamo o njima

294
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:08,460
[SPEAKER_04] i je li ok imat dozu

295
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:11,700
[SPEAKER_04] zezancije...

296
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih rekao iznenađujuće malo

297
00:18:13,519 --> 00:18:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] takvih komentara.

298
00:18:14,460 --> 00:18:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Iznenađujuće malo?

299
00:18:15,559 --> 00:18:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da ja bih očekival da ih ima dosta.

300
00:18:17,099 --> 00:18:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne, ali pa upravo to

301
00:18:19,359 --> 00:18:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] imi smo očekivali da,

302
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno ja bih rekao

303
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] da će ih biti više,

304
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] a jednostavno nije.

305
00:18:23,579 --> 00:18:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] I šta znam,

306
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] osjetili su valjda ljudi

307
00:18:26,079 --> 00:18:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] da ne postoji nekakva loša tu namjera

308
00:18:28,619 --> 00:18:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] i da iskonski ono

309
00:18:31,299 --> 00:18:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] hoćemo nešto dobro, jeli.

310
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, Ksenija Abramojsti

311
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] je najbolji primjer,

312
00:18:35,079 --> 00:18:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je ona u stvari

313
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] i okupila njih, jeli.

314
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:39,160
[SPEAKER_00] I da je ona ono

315
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,240
[SPEAKER_00] kao neko od koga

316
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,759
[SPEAKER_00] ćeš možda prvog očekivati

317
00:18:41,759 --> 00:18:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] da neće biti sad sklon

318
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] naš ono pogotovo

319
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] na svojoj televiziji

320
00:18:45,039 --> 00:18:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ono moraš vagat

321
00:18:46,859 --> 00:18:48,740
[SPEAKER_00] sto komentara

322
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] kakve ćeš možda čuti, jeli.

323
00:18:51,059 --> 00:18:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje moraš biti oprezan.

324
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je ona prva ova

325
00:18:53,779 --> 00:18:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] imala sluha za to.

326
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo,

327
00:18:56,220 --> 00:18:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] ja bih stvarno rekao

328
00:18:57,019 --> 00:18:58,700
